Package mru.tsc.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyInputException
    If the input is empty this exception is thrown.
    MinBiggerThanMaxException
    If the minimum number is larger than the maximum number this exception is thrown.
    NegativeNumberException
    Throw an exception when there is an negative user input.
    NoResultFoundException
    If there is no result found this exception is thrown.
    NotEnoughAvailableCountException
    If the available count is not enough this exception is thrown.
    SerialNumberFormatException
    If the input serial number is not 10-digit long.
    UniqueSerialNumberException
    If the serial number is already in the ArrayList this exception is thrown.
